00051 static void rna_ActionGroup_channels_next(CollectionPropertyIterator *iter)
00052 {
00053     ListBaseIterator *internal = iter->internal;
00054     FCurve *fcu = (FCurve*)internal->link;
00055     bActionGroup *grp = fcu->grp;
00056     
00057     /* only continue if the next F-Curve (if existant) belongs in the same group */
00058     if ((fcu->next) && (fcu->next->grp == grp))
00059         internal->link = (Link*)fcu->next;
00060     else
00061         internal->link = NULL;
00062         
00063     iter->valid = (internal->link != NULL);
00064 }

00071 static void rna_Action_groups_remove(bAction *act, ReportList *reports, bActionGroup *agrp)
00072 {
00073     FCurve *fcu, *fcn;
00074     
00075     /* try to remove the F-Curve from the action */
00076     if (!BLI_remlink_safe(&act->groups, agrp)) {
00077         BKE_reportf(reports, RPT_ERROR, "ActionGroup '%s' not found in action '%s'", agrp->name, act->id.name+2);
00078         return;
00079     }
00080 
00081     /* move every one one of the group's F-Curves out into the Action again */
00082     for (fcu = agrp->channels.first; (fcu) && (fcu->grp == agrp); fcu = fcn) {
00083         fcn = fcu->next;
00084         
00085         /* remove from group */
00086         action_groups_remove_channel(act, fcu);
00087         
00088         /* tack onto the end */
00089         BLI_addtail(&act->curves, fcu);
00090     }
00091     
00092     /* XXX, invalidates PyObject */
00093     MEM_freeN(agrp);
00094 }

00096 static FCurve *rna_Action_fcurve_new(bAction *act, ReportList *reports, const char *data_path,
00097                                      int index, const char *group)
00098 {
00099     if (group && group[0] =='\0') group = NULL;
00100 
00101     if (data_path[0] == '\0') {
00102         BKE_report(reports, RPT_ERROR, "F-Curve data path empty, invalid argument");
00103         return NULL;
00104     }
00105 
00106     /* annoying, check if this exists */
00107     if (verify_fcurve(act, group, data_path, index, 0)) {
00108         BKE_reportf(reports, RPT_ERROR, "F-Curve '%s[%d]' already exists in action '%s'", data_path,
00109                     index, act->id.name+2);
00110         return NULL;
00111     }
00112     return verify_fcurve(act, group, data_path, index, 1);
00113 }
00114 
00115 static void rna_Action_fcurve_remove(bAction *act, ReportList *reports, FCurve *fcu)
00116 {
00117     if (fcu->grp) {
00118         if (BLI_findindex(&act->groups, fcu->grp) == -1) {
00119             BKE_reportf(reports, RPT_ERROR, "F-Curve's ActionGroup '%s' not found in action '%s'",
00120                         fcu->grp->name, act->id.name+2);
00121             return;
00122         }
00123         
00124         action_groups_remove_channel(act, fcu);
00125         free_fcurve(fcu);
00126     }
00127     else {
00128         if (BLI_findindex(&act->curves, fcu) == -1) {
00129             BKE_reportf(reports, RPT_ERROR, "F-Curve not found in action '%s'", act->id.name+2);
00130             return;
00131         }
00132         
00133         BLI_remlink(&act->curves, fcu);
00134         free_fcurve(fcu);
00135     }
00136 }

00201 /* used to check if an action (value pointer) is suitable to be assigned to the ID-block that is ptr */
00202 int rna_Action_id_poll(PointerRNA *ptr, PointerRNA value)
00203 {
00204     ID *srcId = (ID *)ptr->id.data;
00205     bAction *act = (bAction *)value.id.data;
00206     
00207     if (act) {
00208         /* there can still be actions that will have undefined id-root
00209          * (i.e. floating "action-library" members) which we will not
00210          * be able to resolve an idroot for automatically, so let these through
00211          */
00212         if (act->idroot == 0)
00213             return 1;
00214         else if (srcId)
00215             return GS(srcId->name) == act->idroot;
00216     }
00217     
00218     return 0;
00219 }
00220 
00221 /* used to check if an action (value pointer) can be assigned to Action Editor given current mode */
00222 int rna_Action_actedit_assign_poll(PointerRNA *ptr, PointerRNA value)
00223 {
00224     SpaceAction *saction = (SpaceAction *)ptr->data;
00225     bAction *act = (bAction *)value.id.data;
00226     
00227     if (act) {
00228         /* there can still be actions that will have undefined id-root
00229          * (i.e. floating "action-library" members) which we will not
00230          * be able to resolve an idroot for automatically, so let these through
00231          */
00232         if (act->idroot == 0)
00233             return 1;
00234         
00235         if (saction) {
00236             if (saction->mode == SACTCONT_ACTION) {
00237                 /* this is only Object-level for now... */
00238                 return act->idroot == ID_OB;
00239             }
00240             else if (saction->mode == SACTCONT_SHAPEKEY) {
00241                 /* obviously shapekeys only */
00242                 return act->idroot == ID_KE;
00243             }
00244         }
00245     }
00246     
00247     return 0;
00248 }

00438 static void rna_def_action_group(BlenderRNA *brna)
00439 {
00440     StructRNA *srna;
00441     PropertyRNA *prop;
00442

00614     RNA_def_property_collection_sdna(prop, NULL, "markers", NULL);

00623     RNA_def_property_clear_flag(prop, PROP_EDITABLE);

00626      * but is still available/editable in 'emergencies' */

00628     RNA_def_property_enum_sdna(prop, NULL, "idroot");
